snippet.title: Result of Working Full-Time as a Solo Indie Game Dev for 3 Months - CraftyCounty's 1st Devlog
snippet.description:
Welcome to my new video series of weekly Devlogs. This is episode 1 of this series of development log. It's A special episode, where I'll be focusing on introducing you to my main project, instead of summing up the progress of the week. 

All episodes: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLaFbdcIP-CNj0f98D_2oJSjNmrSZEItiy
----------
Find me online: http://links.timkrief.com
----------
All my projects here are proudly made using free/libre open source software:
- Games made using Godot Engine, Blender, Audacity, Gimp etc.
- Videos made using Olive video editor
On a computer that runs thanks to GNU/Linux, Debian, Ubuntu, Gnome and other FLOSS tools.
----------
Musics used from the Youtube Music Library: 
 Edison by Cxdy
 TFB3 by Vibe Tracks
 TFB9 by Vibe Tracks
 Heel Flip by Slynk & Kermode
_____
Photos used from Pexels Photo Library:
 Bird's Eye View Of City by Maxime Francis
 City Buildings during Golden Hour by Adrianna Calvo
 Building With the Word Hope by Jonatan Vanting Iversen
